name: Against All Odds
description:
What if we had a different life in another realm? 
What would you be? Will you be happy?
-
I often imagine a life of my own in a fantasy filled with magic and wonders. Will I find this utopia here in the metaverse? Let’s go!
-
My first artwork on hicetnunc, in celebration of my 36th birthday and #HEN500K .
